citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:00-12:30
on 14-Jun-17.
Arrived at facility to find no responsible adult available to conduct the inspection. Owner was not able to be
contacted via phone call.
